onDomReady
==========

A simple JavaScript onDomReady wrapper mapped to the DOMContentLoaded event.

Basic Usage:
- Add the included script in the HEAD section of your HTML

To use it:



    document.ondomready = function(evt) {

      //Add some code here and may remove code below:

     alert('onDomReady Event has been fired by DOMContentLoaded.');

    };
